https://w3id.org/okn/o/sd#description: This data transformation reformats GLDAS data into the format accepted by TopoFlow (rti and rts). The outputs1 file aggregates rt1 and rts files together, and should be the one used by TopoFlow.
https://w3id.org/okn/o/sd#hasUsageNotes: The GLDAS data has data points every 3 hours, and when selecting it the parameter dt in TopoFlow should be set to 10800
